30:24.310 --> 30:25.440
Begini baru benar.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.070
Ibu.

30:28.920 --> 30:29.380
Begini.

30:30.040 --> 30:30.520
Besok,

30:30.550 --> 30:31.880
